This is the FEAST software package

FEAST stands for Finite Element Analysis for Simulations and Training

---------------------------------------------------------------------

FEASTs main purpose is to be a way of generating large datasets of solved simulations for ML and other usecases.

Its probably not very good icl.

Install with commands:

git clone --recursive-submodules https://github.com/JDList/feast.git
cd feast
cmake -S . -B build
cmake --build build -j

From there python package can be used by including "import feast" in your python file and PYTHONPATH=PATHTOFEAST/feast/python/ before running file or from within this filepath.

- James D. List
